        "*The Bai-Perron procedure detects the structural features visible in the data:\n",
        "a volatility reduction in the mid-1980s (the Great Moderation), and shifts\n",
        "in the mean growth rate across the sample. The break dates recovered by the\n",
        "algorithm should be compared with the 1984 Q1 prior from the Chow and QLR\n",
        "tests — alignment across methods strengthens the case that the detected break\n",
        "is a genuine feature of the process rather than a statistical artefact. Where\n",
